thread.title: Kennedy Wilson to Announce First Quarter 2018 Earnings

author: cnbc.com
title: Kennedy Wilson to Announce First Quarter 2018 Earnings
text:
Company to hold conference call and webcast to discuss first quarter financial results
BEVERLY HILLS, Calif.--(BUSINESS WIRE)-- Global real estate investment company Kennedy Wilson ( NYSE: KW ) will release its first quarter 2018 financial results on Wednesday, May 2, 2018 after the market closes. The company will hold a live conference call and webcast to discuss results at 7:00 a.m. PT/10:00 a.m. ET on Thursday, May 3, 2018.
The direct dial-in number for the conference call is (844) 340-4761 for U.S. callers and (412) 717-9616 for international callers.
A replay of the call will be available for one week beginning one hour after the live call and can be accessed at (877) 344-7529 for U.S. callers and (412) 317-0088 for international callers. The passcode for the replay is 10119071 .
The webcast will be available at: https://services.choruscall.com/links/kw180503QTkCcn5z.html . A replay of the webcast will be available one hour after the original webcast on the Companyâ€™s investor relations web site for three months.
About Kennedy Wilson
Kennedy Wilson is a leading global real estate investment company. We own, operate, and invest in real estate both on our own and through our investment management platform. We focus on multifamily and office properties located in the Western U.S., the U.K., and Ireland. For further information on Kennedy Wilson, please visit: www.kennedywilson.com .
